%% decisions: D-PL-1 worker 1 直列実行, D-PL-2 hooks=submodule権威, D-PL-3 cwd=. 厳守
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> CopyADR: start
    CopyADR --> CopyPhases: adr copied
    CopyPhases --> CopyHooks: phases copied
    CopyHooks --> CopyCommands: hooks copied
    CopyCommands --> CopyRules: commands copied
    CopyRules --> FixMcp: rules copied
    FixMcp --> Commit: mcp fixed cwd=.
    Commit --> Push: commit-sha acquired
    Push --> Done: origin/main updated
    Done --> [*]
    CopyADR --> Failed: error
    CopyPhases --> Failed: error
    CopyHooks --> Failed: error
    CopyCommands --> Failed: error
    CopyRules --> Failed: error
    FixMcp --> Failed: mcp mismatch
    Commit --> Failed: hook block
    Push --> Failed: remote reject
    Failed --> [*]
